Duties (Concession Extension) Order 2023

I make the following order under sections 46B and 46K of the Duties Act 2001 .

22 May 2023

MICHAEL DARREL JOSEPH FERGUSON

Treasurer

1. Short title
    This order may be cited as the Duties (Concession Extension) Order 2023 .

2. Commencement
    This order takes effect on the day on which its making is notified in the Gazette.

3. Principal Act
    In this order, the Duties Act 2001 is referred to as the Principal Act.

4.
    The amendment effected by this clause has been incorporated into the authorised version of the Duties Act 2001 .

5.
    The amendment effected by this clause has been incorporated into the authorised version of the Duties Act 2001 .

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 31 May 2023

This order is administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
